</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:47
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96148' id='t-96148'>And I say, &quot;In theory, it's possible.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='97994' id='t-97994'>&quot;Thank you, bye.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:50
