<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='100251' id='t-100251'>Five minutes later, the headline on BBC:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='103473' id='t-103473'>&quot;Scientist claims
