<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='106632' id='t-106632'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='109152' id='t-109152'>Within minutes, the entire world
