</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 2:09
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='118051' id='t-118051'>It doesn't matter how much I explained
