<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='197172' id='t-197172'>to dress up like Sigmund Freud.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:31
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='200299' id='t-200299'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 3:32
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='201592' id='t-201592'>So now there is not only
just a story about me</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='203855' id='t-203855'>but also a nice visual to go with it,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='206435' id='t-206435'>and I am deemed by the media now
